chat.msg: hi there, empezamos?
si!
brilliant! I'm at the starting point, I see a twig on the left that leads to an island with a tiger
where are we going?
sigues to the left, donde stas el tiger
okay, i'm on the tiger's island now
debo seguir for the islands of the butterfly or the parrot?
tienes que seguir to the parrot
got it
i'm at the big island with the parrot on a tree. where should i go next, towards the frog or the elephant?
you can go to the elephante
Perfecto, ahora estoy en el elefante.
¿Me dirijo al cocodrilo o voy directamente a la jirafa?
tienes que ir a la giraffe!
alrighty, i'm at the giraffe now
snake's to the southeast, do i keep going that way?
si sigues
now i'm at the snake
fat little fellow he is! where to next?
keep moving forward, ayi estas tu destination
awesome! two steps east and voila, i'm at the treasure
¡lo conseguimos! *finished*
hi there, empezamos?
si!
awesome! so right now you should be near the white dog. let's take a little stroll. walk a bit to your left, under a wooden bench, and cross a trail heading towards a florist stand
don't actually go to the florist, though. make a swift u-turn and head back towards our furry friend. got it?
No problema!
excellent! now, see that branch across the trail? cross it and continue heading southward
there's another white dog by a picnic blanket. head that way
okay, ya voy para el branch. do I keep going to the left after I pass el perro blanco?
nop, not just yet
go over the picnic blanket, passing a bowl of delicious berries. then continue heading west, amigo
Ok estoy aki where the berries are, where to ahora?
alright! look for a branch that'll take you north, over the river
go over that
towards la gente en la bicicleta?
yes, but don't touch that green bush
circle it from your right and you'll find that florist stand we talked about
ok i am near the florist, ahora que?
cool! now go to the left, get below that stand, and start heading towards a big bridge with two cyclists on it
stand behind the florist stand?
¡sí correcto! Luego continúa hacia el oeste pasando el puente.
ok, y ahora?
great! you're doing so well
just past the bridge, there are some old folks on a bench. get close to them but then head south
ok i see a deer, ahora que??
wait, don't move! you're almost there! now, veer a bit to the east, between a wooden branch and a bush
got it?
hi there! que comience el juego!!
okay, tienes que ir straight ahead, y vaz aver un perro
super, veo al perro sentado a la izquierda del fuego
¿hacia dónde me dirijo después?
tienes que ir donde stas el fuego y los hongos
ready! I am by the fire and the red mushrooms
and now that?
go between the fire and mushrooms, head east towards a un carro azul, and stop
okay, now i'm at the blue car
what's next, mate?
tienes que ir to the left, and head downwards until and stop when you are next to the second bush to your right
done! i'm now next to a blue telescope with some rocks and a house to my west
sigues west, ayi estas tu destination
whoohoo! i made it to the wooden house surrounded by rocks
*finished* thanks for guiding me, mate! what's next on our game night?
hi there! que comience el juego!!
ok, veo un perro marron ahead of me, do i go that way?
correcto, amigo! pero antes de llegar al cachorro, gira un poco a la izquierda y luego, a la derecha
ahora estás yendo al sur
ok, ahora que?
vas a ver un par de rocas, una grande a tu izquierda y una pequeña a tu derecha
pasa entre ellas hasta llegar al agua
ok, veo el agua. donde voy ahora?
chévere! métete al agua, vea un cangrejo rojo frente a ti
luego, gira a tu derecha y sigue la gran roca. vas a estar moviéndote hacia el oeste ahora
ok estoy donde el oeste
¡genial! ahora busca una roca de tamaño medio
una vez que la veas, sigue adelante hasta que veas un tiburón
ok veo el tiburon, que susto! huye tell me where to go
¡no te asustes, sólo es un juego! haz una curva acentuada a la derecha y dirígete de vuelta a tierra
ya! omg im still alive. ok veo un volleyball.
¡hahaha, sobreviviste al tiburón! ahora, encuentra la roca mediana y el balón de volleyball
¿ves esos dos?
si
fantastic! pass between them and continue north
ok veo un speaker, musica maestro lol, ahora donde voy?
hahaha, sigue la música! ve hacia el noroeste, atravesando entre una carpa roja y ese altavoz grande
valle, ahora que?
Now, you have to go around the tent in an arc
keep moving until you're heading back south
ok i see a canoe
¡perfecto! Ahora gira a la derecha y pasa por debajo del kayak rojo.
listo, ahora donde?
good job! finally, turn right (north) and walk alongside the kayak until you find a small green bush
You are very close to the goal! You see it?
